high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right to face the potato on the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Turn around and cross the room to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and cross the room to face the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Step to the right to face the fridge.
Cool the potato slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around and cross the room to face the microwave.
Place the potato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool a potato slice and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn to the right and face the potato.
Slice the potato with the knife.
Turn around and take the knife to the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Walk back to where the potato is.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Walk to the the fridge with the potato slice.
Put the potato in the fridge then take it back out.
Walk back to the microwave.
Place the potato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place the chilled potato slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn right to the counter
SLice the potato on the counter
Turn around, go to the microwave
Put the knife in the microwave
Turn around, go to the counter
Pick up a potato slice from the counter
Turn right, go to the fridge
Put the potato slice in the fridge, wait, pick up the potato slice from the fridge
Turn left, go forward, turn left and go to the microwave
Put the potato slice in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, cool a slice in the fridge
